title: Apocalypse Sword God
description: Apocalypse Sword God Manhua 末日剑神：我震惊全球！Doomsday Sword God If mercy and kindness can’t save the world, then this time, I choose to kill— Eternal Slayer! Heavenly Lightning Slash! Sword of Annihilation! As long as you learn the most common sword skills, they can be upgraded to SSS rank?! Divine talent + forbidden skills! I’m the last spark of hope in this apocalypse!
